      "author": {
        "_account_id": 6,
        "name": "Cory Spitz",
        "email": "cory.spitz@hpe.com",
        "username": "spitzcor"
      },
      "date": "2020-02-27 18:09:49.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> I would also ask that everyone at HPE update the email addresses in their accounts in Gerrit rather than creating new accounts. There are already too many duplicates due various people, I don't really want to see more.\nI sent out instructions to everyone at Cray/HPE about how to do this.  So, we *should* all be moved over to our hpe.com addresses without creating duplicate accounts.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
